rename columns from vector for new names

rename columns from vector for new names

rename_cols(.df, new_names)

Arguments

.df
dataframe to rename
new_names
vector of names using syntax "<newname>" = "<oldname>"

Examples

rename_cols(Theoph, c("dv" = "conc", "ID" = "Subject"))
